name: Antonelli Maxi Chocolate Cream Filled Croissant - 80 g / 2.82 oz
description:
A delectable creation from Antonelli Industrie Dolciarie, renowned for their expertise in crafting exquisite pastries. This particular offering is a supersized croissant, making it a substantial treat for any occasion.

What sets this pastry apart is its sumptuous filling of smooth and indulgent chocolate cream. The richness of the chocolate combined with the flakiness of the croissant creates a heavenly combination of flavors and textures that is sure to delight the palate.

The versatility of this pastry makes it an ideal choice for various occasions. Whether enjoyed as a quick and convenient breakfast alongside a steaming cup of coffee to kickstart the day or savored as a satisfying snack to indulge in during a break, it promises to satisfy cravings and provide a moment of pure enjoyment.

name: Bambi Lane Biscuits - 300 g
description: Made with simple, pure ingredients, including wheat flour, sugar, honey and milk, Plazma biscuits are enriched with anti-oxidants, vitamins and minerals. With calcium, iron, zinc, vitamins C and B6, niacin and thiamine in the recipe, these classic cookies are often enjoyed as meal replacements. Sweet - but not too sweet - with a taste akin to graham crackers and a crumbly texture, Plazma biscuits are perfect for dunking in milk, tea or coffee and wonderful with Eurocrem, Nutella or jam. Generations of families have grown up with these delicious little treats.

name: Brandt Rusk Bread -225g
description: Brandt is the # 1 manufacturer of Zwieback worldwide. Zwieback is a crispy, sweetened bread made with eggs and baked twice. It is sliced before it is baked for the second time, which then results in a crispy, brittle slice that closely resembles melba toast or rusk. Although commonly used for teething children, it also makes a nice breakfast snack which one can use with butter, cream cheese, jelly and peanut butter for example. Medicinally, Zwieback is very good for upset stomachs, as it absorbs acid.

name: Burger Rusk Bread-225g
description: Burger's Zwieback Rusks are a delightful crispy bread, sweetened and crafted with eggs, then baked twice. A cherished item found in every German household, they evoke nostalgic childhood memories. These rusks are commonly enjoyed with coffee or softened in milk to create a beloved porridge, often a favorite among children. Each box holds around 24 delicious rusks, perfect for savoring these traditional treats.

name: Dora Pastry Cream Filled Croissant - 300 g ( 6 pcs )
description:
Indulge in the exquisite craftsmanship of Italian pastry-making with Antonelli Industrie Dolciarie's fine creation. Encased within each box are six treasures, individually wrapped to preserve their freshness and flavor, awaiting your enjoyment.

As you unwrap these delicacies, you're greeted by the aroma of buttery, flaky croissants, each one filled with a sumptuous pastry cream. This velvety filling, crafted with precision and care, offers a luxurious contrast to the light, airy texture of the croissant, creating a symphony of flavors and textures that dance upon your palate.

These delectable pastries are not just a treat for the taste buds; they're also a convenient option for busy mornings or leisurely afternoons. Paired with a steaming cup of coffee, they make for a perfect breakfast, infusing your day with a touch of indulgence and sophistication. Alternatively, enjoy them as a delightful snack, whether you're taking a break from work or simply craving a moment of culinary delight.

With each bite, savor the essence of Italian tradition and expertise that permeates every aspect of these pastries. From the flaky layers of the croissant to the creamy richness of the pastry cream filling, each element reflects the mastery and dedication of Antonelli Industrie Dolciarie's artisans.

So go ahead, unwrap these delectable treats, and immerse yourself in the unparalleled pleasure they offer. Whether enjoyed as a quick breakfast or a leisurely snack, let these croissants transport you to the streets of Italy, where the art of pastry-making is celebrated and cherished. Buon Appetito!

description:
This delectable pastry, crafted by the renowned Italian group Antonelli Industrie Dolciarie, embodies the essence of indulgence and sophistication. Each box unveils a treasure trove of six meticulously crafted croissants, each one meticulously wrapped to preserve its freshness and flavor.

At the heart of these pastries lies a symphony of flavors - a luscious pistachio and chocolate cream filling, expertly blended to create a harmonious balance of richness and sweetness. The velvety pistachio cream intertwines with the decadent chocolate, creating a sensory delight that tantalizes the taste buds with every bite.

Perfect for those busy mornings when time is of the essence, these croissants offer a convenient and satisfying breakfast option. Paired with a steaming cup of coffee, they provide a comforting start to the day, infusing it with a touch of Italian elegance and flavor. Alternatively, they serve as a delightful snack, offering a moment of indulgence to be savored at any time.

With each bite, savor the craftsmanship and dedication that goes into creating these fine pastries. Whether enjoyed as a breakfast treat or a midday indulgence, let these croissants transport you to the streets of Italy, where the art of pastry-making is revered and cherished. So go ahead, unwrap, savor, and enjoy the simple pleasures that Antonelli Industrie Dolciarie has to offer. Buon Appetito!

name: Dr. Oetker Extra Gelier Zucher 2 : 1 -500g
description:
With Dr. Oetker Extra Gelling Sugar 2: 1 you can make extra fruity and less sweet jams, and jellies. For a pack of extra gelling sugar (500 g) you need 1,000 g of fruit or 900 ml of fruit juice. It is also possible to use any commercially available juice or nectar to make a jelly (with the exception of grape juice).
Dr. Oetker Extra Gelling Sugar contains the herbal gelling agent pectin, which is obtained from apples and citrus fruits. Since the gelling agent and sugar are already mixed, preparation is particularly quick and easy - ideal for beginners.
Sweet but also savory preserves are possible with Dr. Oetker Extra Preserving Sugar 2: 1 guaranteed.

name: Dr. Oetker Gustin-400g
description: Gustin fine cornstarch Content: 400 g For refining cakes, tarts and biscuits and for binding hot liquids Basic preparation for baked goods: Simply replace 1/3 of the wheat flour amount specified in the recipe with Gustin. This gives the baked goods a particularly fine structure. Basic preparation for binding liquids: Weigh out the appropriate amount of Gustin and stir until smooth with some of the respective cold amount of liquid. Bring the remaining liquid to the boil, stir in the mixed Gustin with a whisk and bring everything to the boil again while stirring. Food Ingredients Gustin sponge and sponge cakes, eg marble cakes, sand cakes, cake bases according to the quantities in the recipe, replace 1/3 of the amount of flour with Gustin. For cake fillings e.g. B.

name: Dr. Oetker Raspberry Cream Dessert -62 g
description:
Wonderfully creamy dessert pleasure with the typically delicious raspberry-cream flavor of the classic cake.The raspberry cream has sophistication: If you like the raspberry-cream cake, then you will love this dessert.
Delight your friends or family with the fine fruity note of raspberries. And you don't have to spend a lot of time preparing it. The raspberry cream from Dr. Oetker is quick and easy to make: you just have to whip up the dessert powder with some cold milk and then put it in the fridge. After the short cooling time, the raspberry cream is ready to be enjoyed. Round off the dessert with raspberries or other berries. This gives the raspberry cream from Dr. Oetker an additional fresh nuance.

name: Dr. Oetker Sweet Meal Apfel Pufferchen -125g
description:
These light, juicy dough puffs with a fruity apple flavor are quick and easy to prepare! The dough for the delicious apple puff mixture with the fruity little apple pieces from Dr. Oetker is ready to serve in just ten minutes.
Stir 150 ml milk into the Dr. Oetker apple puff mixture, add an egg and then bake the sweet apple puffs in the pan. Then serve the warm, delicious apple puffs with powdered sugar, cinnamon sugar or delicious applesauce, depending on your taste.

name: Dr. Oetker Sweet Meal Milchreis ( Rice Pudding ) -125g
description:
Classic style rice pudding
The classic that you can refine as you wish. Whether with cinnamon and sugar, Dr. Oetker fruit groats from the refrigerated shelf, fresh fruit or applesauce - Dr. Oetker Sweet Meal Classic-style rice pudding always works and tastes good! Our tip: fold 100 g of stiffly whipped cream into the rice pudding and serve it with apricot pieces and raisins.
The preparation is very simple, the dish known from childhood is ready in just 10 minutes. No burning or boiling over of the milk! Whether as a main meal or in between: Dr. Oetker sweet meal tastes as good as homemade!

name: Dr. Oetker Sweet Meal Griessbrei ( Semolina Porridge ) -92g
description:
Classic style semolina porridge
Conjure up the good old days on your lunch table in no time, because Dr. Oetker sweet meal semolina porridge is prepared in just 5 minutes! You boil 500 ml of milk, remove it from the heat and add the semolina porridge. Stir, leave covered for 5 minutes and it's ready. No burning or boiling over of the milk!
Enjoy Dr. Oetker sweet meal semolina porridge warm or cold with Dr. Oetker fruit groats from the refrigerated shelf, fresh berries or cherry compote. Whether as a main meal or in between: Dr. Oetker sweet meal tastes as good as homemade!

name: Leicht & Cross Rye Crispbread-125 g ( Best if used by 02/01/2024 )
description:
Leight & Cross rye goes particularly well with savory toppings such as cheese , tomatoes or turkey breast but it also tastes good when served sweetly. This fibre-rich crunchy disc is particularly popular because of its strong aroma. Try something exotic and top your crispy rye slice with brie, persimmon and thyme.

Ingredients
Rye flour, wheat flour, whole grain rye flour, malted wheat flour , sugar, sunflower oil, salt.
To make 100g of crispy rye bread, 52g of rye flour and 22g of wholemeal rye flour are used.
